00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.500
Tim Tam Cupcakes

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.500
Serves: 8 cupcakes

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:17.500
Equipment: a muffin tin and 8 paper cups

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:19.500
Ingredients for the cupcakes :

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:22.000
25 g (¼ cup) cocoa powder

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.800
125 ml (½ cup) boiling water

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:28.000
100 g (⅔ cup) flour

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.700
1 tsp baking powder 

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:31.000
Pinch of salt

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:34.000
60 g (¼ cup) butter, softened

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:35.800
100 g (½ cup) sugar

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:37.000
1 large egg

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
1 tsp vanilla extract

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.200
1 pack of TimTam

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:41.200
Ingredients for the chocolate frosting :

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:45.200
120 g (⅔ cup) unsweetened chocolate, chopped

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:48.200
150 g (⅔ cup) butter, softened

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:51.800
150 g (1 ⅓  cup) powdered sugar, sifted

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:54.200
2 tsp pure vanilla extract

00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:55.800
4 Tim Tam fingers

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.800
Directions for the cupcakes :

00:00:57.800 --> 00:01:04.000
Preheat the oven to 180°C and place the paper cups into the muffin tin. 

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:11.000
In a small bowl stir the boiling hot water and the cocoa powder until smooth then let cool.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:18.500
In another bowl, whisk together the flour, baking powder, and salt.

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:24.000
Beat the butter and sugar until light and fluffy. 

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:29.000
Add the egg، beating until smooth. 

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:31.800
Beat in the vanilla extract. 

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:35.700
Add the flour mixture and beat only until incorporated.

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:40.800
Then add the cooled cocoa mixture and stir until smooth.

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:46.300
Cut the Tim Tam into small pieces then stir into the batter.

00:01:46.300 --> 00:01:50.500
Fill each muffin cup about two-thirds full with batter.

00:01:50.500 --> 00:02:00.200
and bake for about 16 to 20 minutes then remove from oven and place on a wire rack to cool

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:01.800
Directions for the Chocolate Frosting : 

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:06.800
Melt the chocolate in a bowl placed over a saucepan of simmering water then remove from heat and let cool.

00:02:06.800 --> 00:02:10.000
In the bowl of your electric mixer, or with a hand mixer, beat the butter until smooth and creamy

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:15.000
then add the sugar and beat until it is light and fluffy, about 2 minutes.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:18.000
Beat in the vanilla extract.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:25.800
Add the chocolate and beat on low speed until well combined. and beat until frosting is smooth and glossy

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.000
To decorate the cupcakes :

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:33.000
Once the cupcakes have completely cooled, frost with icing.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:38.000
Cut the 4 Tim Tam fingers in half and decorate each cupcake with half a finger.

